1. HTML Structure (profile.html):

html
Copy code
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="profile.css">
    <title>Whitespace - Profile</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <!-- Centered title -->
        <h1 id="site-title">Whitespace</h1>
        
        <!-- Navigation bar centered below the title -->
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="browse.html">Browse</a></li>
                <li><a href="post.html">Post</a></li>
                <li><a href="login.html">Log In/Sign Up</a></li>
                <li><a href="profile.html">Profile</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <!-- Content for the Profile Page -->
        <section id="user-profile">
            <!-- Add elements for user profile display/edit here -->
            <h2>User Profile</h2>
            <!-- Add user profile information or edit options here -->
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <!-- Footer content if needed -->
        <p>&copy; 2024 Whitespace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <!-- JavaScript file -->
    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
2. CSS Styling (profile.css):

css
Copy code
/* profile.css */

/* Reset some default styles */
body, h1, h2, h3, p, ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #f2f2f2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100vh; /* 100% viewport height */
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1em;
    width: 100%;
}

#site-title {
    font-size: 2em;
}

nav ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    margin-top: 10px; /* Add some spacing between title and navigation */
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin-right: 20px;
}

main {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 20px auto;
    padding: 20px;
}

#user-profile {
    text-align: center;
}

#user-profile h2 {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px;
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
}
